[{"type":"{{","value":[["pagebanner"],["Pagebanner default.jpg"],["pgname=Belmont"]]},"\n",{"type":"'''","value":["Belmont"]}," is a town in ",{"type":"[[","value":[["North Carolina"]]},".\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get in"]},"\n\nBelmont is located west of Charlotte, in the south-central part of North Carolina.  It is most easily accessed by either ",{"type":"'''","value":["I-85"]}," or ",{"type":"'''","value":["NC-74"]},".  \n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Get around"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["See"]},"\n\nBelmont's most prominent sight is the Gothic architecture of Belmont Abbey College.  It is viewable from NC-74, and worth a brief side trip.\n\nThere is a 1950s-style drive-in movie theater on the outskirts of town.  This attraction is both ",{"type":"''","value":["extremely"]}," cheap and fun, especially as a family or date activity. \n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Do"]},"\n\nThe Daniel Stowe Botanical Garden is located in Belmont.  This large outdoor garden attracts tourists from around the region, and is especially attractive during the springtime.  \n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Buy"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Eat"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Drink"]},"\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Sleep"]},"\nFound inside of Belmont is the Hampton Inn, a fancy hotel located right next to a Ford dealership!\n\n",{"type":"==","value":["Go next"]},"\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["routebox"],["image1=I-85.svg"],["imagesize1=22"],["directionl1=S"],["majorl1=",{"type":"[[","value":[["Spartanburg"]]}],["minorl1=",{"type":"[[","value":[["Gastonia"]]}],["directionr1=N"],["majorr1=",{"type":"[[","value":[["Greensboro"]]}],["minorr1=",{"type":"[[","value":[["Charlotte"]]}],["image2=US 29.svg"],["imagesize2=22"],["image2a=US 74.svg"],["imagesize2a=22"],["directionl2=S\/W"],["majorl2=",{"type":"[[","value":[["Spartanburg"]]},"\/",{"type":"[[","value":[["Asheville"]]}],["minorl2=",{"type":"[[","value":[["Gastonia"]]}],["directionr2=N\/E"],["majorr2=",{"type":"[[","value":[["Greensboro"]]},"\/",{"type":"[[","value":[["Lumberton"]]}],["minorr2=",{"type":"[[","value":[["Charlotte"]]}]]},"\n\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["geo"],["35.244444"],["-81.035556"]]},"\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["outlinecity"]]},"\n",{"type":"{{","value":[["IsPartOf"],["Piedmont (North Carolina)"]]},"\n",{"type":"[[","value":[["Wikipedia:Belmont, North Carolina"]]}]